
  C H A N G E S 
 ===============

This file contains a list of all changes to the simulator.

Mar 16th 2008
 - added macros that allow the Simulator to stay native even when using
   function pointers, method pointers, or RAM hooks to those

Mar 13th 2008
 - added naked classes TTask and TMonitor
 - added new functions

Mar 11th 2008
 - implemented more simulated functions
 - added code to call the emulator from within the simulator code
 
Mar 10th 2008
 - fixed project files for MSWindows / VisualC 8
 - updated project files for OS X / XCode
 
Mar 5th 2008
 - added code to access emulated RAM (no MMU handling yet)
 - added macros to support class member access under emulation and simulation
 - added more sample implementations

Feb 29th 2008
 - initial release of simulator
 - added simulatro interface into emulator
 - added native FixedMultiply() function

